ygData.messageBody:
I was just wondering if anybody has done the Deepwater Harpoon quest. I
think it would be really cool to go /anon and pretend to be a Paladin
(especially for me 'cause I'm a DE ;)) I heard that if a cleric swings it it
only does like 1 point of damage, but I just want it for the looks (and hey,
+5 WIS ain't bad) I am on a Paladin email list and they have pretty much
summed up how to get it, I would just like any first-hand experience from
the Clerics out there that might have one. Thanks...

Drizben D'Vorn
Defiled High Priest of Innoruuk
Oblivion Knight of the 30th Circle
